snippet.title: Ace of Spades: Battle Builder Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The official Ace of Spades: Battle Builder trailer

Find out more at: http://www.aceofspades.com

Ace of spades is a creative shooter where you can create your battleground, destroy it, then create it again. It's construction, combat and creativity.
• Endlessly evolving battleground
• Class-based FPS mayhem
• Construct tunnels, fortresses, anything
• Tons of in-game game modes
• Strategise for victory
